The '''Deputy Prime Minister''' was the second-in-command to the [[Prime Minister (Bakura)|Prime Minister of Bakura]]. Most likely it was assistant head of government in the [[Bakuran Senate|senate]]. What became of the position during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial era]] is unknown. [[Blaine Harris]] held the position during the tenure of [[Molierre Cundertol]].

